skdetail:

Invocation Name: my inventory
des:
Keep forgetting where you left things? My Inventory can help with that! 

All those times that you put something in a safe place and then can't remember where it is - just tell My Inventory where it is and it will remember for you!

Lent a DVD to a friend? Tell My Inventory and you'll never forget who has it!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
